OL,3,CCampaign group loses bid to challenge
OL,4,Cplans to upgrade A66
OL,6,FA transport campaign group has lost
OL,7,Fits legal bid to challenge government
OL,8,Fplans to upgrade the A66.
OL,10,FThe A66, which connects Redcar with
OL,11,FWorkington, currently has around 18
OL,12,Fmiles of single-carriageway between
OL,13,FScotch Corner and Penrith.
OL,15,FThe previous conservative Transport
OL,16,FSecretary Mark Harper approved the
OL,17,Fdualling of the A66 between Scotch
OL,18,FCorner and Penrith, in March 2024.
