OL,3,CCampaign group loses bid to challenge
OL,4,Cplans to upgrade A66
OL,6,FTransport Action Network claim the
OL,7,F#1.5bn project will increase carbon
OL,8,Femissions by 2.7m tonnes.
OL,10,FMr Justice Mould dismissed the High
OL,11,FCourt case on 25 October 2024.
OL,13,FIn a ruling, the judge said the bid
OL,14,F"does not raise an arguable basis" to
OL,15,Fclaim the Secretary of State was wrong
OL,16,Fto approve the order.
