OL,6,FHe said: "The Secretary of State
OL,7,Fplainly took into account the need for
OL,8,Fthe development in terms of national
OL,9,Fconsiderations and he also took
OL,10,Faccount of the prospects and
OL,11,Fopportunities of carrying out the
OL,12,Fdevelopment elsewhere."
OL,14,FThe upgrades are expected to see a
OL,15,F30km stretch of single-carriageway
OL,16,Fdualled between junction 40 of the M6
OL,17,Fmotorway at Penrith, Cumbria, and
OL,18,Fjunction 53 of the A1(M) at Scotch
OL,19,FCorner in North Yorkshire.
