OL,4,Cplans to upgrade A66
OL,6,FThe Transport Action Network say the
OL,7,Fscheme would reduce the "tranquillity"
OL,8,Fof the areas surrounding the North
OL,9,FPennines National Landscape.
OL,11,FIt also said air pollution would harm
OL,12,Fblanket bog, an endangered habitat,
OL,13,Fand more than 18,200 trees would be
OL,14,Ffelled.
